    {
      "id": "subtitle-text",
      "type": "text",
      "content": "Should We Build a Native Mobile App?",
      "x": 200,
      "y": 170,
      "width": 1200,
      "style": { "fontSize": 28, "color": "#FFC107" }
    },
    {
      "id": "decision-meta",
      "type": "shape",
      "content": "Owner: CPO Yuki Tanaka | Stakeholders: CEO, CTO, VP Eng, VP Product | Deadline: March 15, 2026",
      "shape": "rectangle",
      "x": 2600,
      "y": 100,
      "width": 2100,
      "height": 70,
      "style": {
        "fillColor": "#283593",
        "fontColor": "#FFFFFF",
        "borderColor": "#FFC107"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "context-frame",
      "type": "frame",
      "title": "Context & Decision Criteria",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 450,
      "width": 4800,
      "height": 350,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#F5F5F5" }
    },
    {
      "id": "context-text",
      "type": "shape",
      "content": "Context: Mobile usage growing industry-wide. Our mobile web lags. Competitors A and C have native apps. Web-only risks losing field teams.\n\nCriteria: Strategic alignment (30%) | Market demand (25%) | Tech feasibility (20%) | ROI (15%) | Risk (10%)\n\nData: 44% survey want mobile | 8% current usage (declining) | 2 of 3 competitors have native apps",
      "shape": "rectangle",
      "x": 150,
      "y": 480,
      "width": 4650,
      "height": 250,
      "style": {
        "fillColor": "#FFFFFF",
        "fontColor": "#212121",
        "borderColor": "#1A237E"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "decision-1",
      "type": "shape",
      "content": "DECISION 1\nIs mobile demand strong enough?\n>20% usage OR >40% survey demand?\n\nResult: 8% usage (NO) but 44% survey (YES)\nForward-looking signal is YES",
      "shape": "diamond",
      "x": 1800,
      "y": 850,
      "width": 700,
      "height": 400,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#FFC107", "fontColor": "#212121" }
    },
    {
      "id": "outcome-a",
      "type": "shape",
      "content": "OUTCOME A: STOP\nDon't build. Monitor quarterly.\nRe-evaluate if usage >15% or survey >50%.\n\nRisk: Market window may close.\nCost of inaction: 5-8% revenue at risk",
      "shape": "rectangle",
      "x": 3200,
      "y": 900,
      "width": 900,
      "height": 300,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#D32F2F", "fontColor": "#FFFFFF" }
    },
    {
      "id": "decision-2",
      "type": "shape",
      "content": "DECISION 2\nDo we have mobile eng talent?\n\nCurrent: 0 dedicated mobile eng\n2 with iOS side-project exp\nBudget for 4 hires approved\n\nResult: PARTIAL",
      "shape": "diamond",
      "x": 400,
      "y": 1300,
      "width": 700,
      "height": 400,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#FFC107", "fontColor": "#212121" }
    },
    {
      "id": "outcome-b",
      "type": "shape",
      "content": "OUTCOME B: PIVOT\nHire mobile team, then build.\nM1-2: Hire 2 iOS + 1 Android + 1 designer\nM3-5: Build MVP\nM6-8: Ship v1.0\nM9-12: Iterate + offline mode\n\nBudget: $1.2M | Impact: +8% MAU",
      "shape": "rectangle",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 1800,
      "width": 900,
      "height": 350,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#FF8F00", "fontColor": "#FFFFFF" }
    },
    {
      "id": "outcome-c",
      "type": "shape",
      "content": "OUTCOME C: EXPLORE\nPartner with mobile dev agency.\nRFP to 3 agencies, select by April 1.\nShip MVP by July.\n\nBudget: $500K + $150K/yr\nRisk: Less control, dependency",
      "shape": "rectangle",
      "x": 1100,
      "y": 1800,
      "width": 900,
      "height": 350,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#1565C0", "fontColor": "#FFFFFF" }
    },
    {
      "id": "decision-3",
      "type": "shape",
      "content": "DECISION 3\nBuild native or cross-platform?\n\nNative: $1.4M, 9-12mo, best UX\nReact Native: $700K, 5-7mo, good UX\nWhite-label: $200K/yr, 2mo, limited",
      "shape": "diamond",
      "x": 2200,
      "y": 1750,
      "width": 700,
      "height": 400,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#FFC107", "fontColor": "#212121" }
    },
    {
      "id": "outcome-d",
      "type": "shape",
      "content": "OUTCOME D: BUILD NATIVE\nSwift (iOS) + Kotlin (Android)\nBest UX, full capabilities, App Store\nBudget: $1.4M | Timeline: 9-12mo\nRequires 6 dedicated engineers\n\nRisk: Longest timeline, dual codebase",
      "shape": "rectangle",
      "x": 3100,
      "y": 1800,
      "width": 850,
      "height": 350,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#43A047", "fontColor": "#FFFFFF" }
    },
    {
      "id": "outcome-e",
      "type": "shape",
      "content": "OUTCOME E: CROSS-PLATFORM\nReact Native — RECOMMENDED\nSingle codebase, faster, cheaper\nBudget: $700K | Timeline: 5-7mo\nHire 3 RN engineers\n\nBest balance of speed, cost, quality",
      "shape": "rectangle",
      "x": 4000,
      "y": 1800,
      "width": 850,
      "height": 350,
      "style": {
        "fillColor": "#43A047",
        "fontColor": "#FFFFFF",
        "borderColor": "#FFC107"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "recommended-badge",
      "type": "shape",
      "content": "RECOMMENDED",
      "shape": "rectangle",
      "x": 4200,
      "y": 1750,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 40,
      "style": { "fillColor": "#FFC107", "fontColor": "#1A237E" }
    },
