      "x": 150,
      "y": 2270,
      "width": 800,
      "style": { "fontSize": 24, "fontWeight": "bold", "color": "#1A237E" }
    },
    {
      "id": "log-content",
      "type": "shape",
      "content": "Date: March 6, 2026\nDecision: Build cross-platform (React Native) — Outcome E\n\nRationale: Survey demand 44% exceeds threshold. RN balances speed, cost, quality. 3 RN hires feasible within Q1 budget.\n\nDissent: CTO preferred native for performance. Agreed to revisit after v1.0 if <60fps.\n\nReview: Re-evaluate after v1.0 ship (August 2026)\nSigned: CPO, CEO, CTO, VP Eng",
      "shape": "rectangle",
      "x": 150,
      "y": 2330,
      "width": 2250,
      "height": 350,
      "style": {
        "fillColor": "#FFFFFF",
        "fontColor": "#212121",
        "borderColor": "#1A237E"
